07:22:38.220 --> 07:22:38.700
tribes.

07:22:38.759 --> 07:22:40.919
So we wanted to give you some basic

07:22:40.919 --> 07:22:43.139
information that may be useful as you get

07:22:43.139 --> 07:22:43.799
to know one another.

07:22:43.860 --> 07:22:46.979
You have been assigned to a winglet with

07:22:46.979 --> 07:22:48.060
6 other dragons.

